\c 23
\s UPawuli ephambi komphakathi
\p
\v 1 UPawuli wasewujolozela\x + Luka 4.20.\x* umphakathi\x + 22.30.\x* wathi: Madoda bazalwane, mina ngihambile\x + Fil. 1.27. Fil. 3.20.\x* phambi kukaNkulunkulu ngesazela sonke esihle\x + 24.16. 2 Kor. 1.12.4.2. 2 Tim. 1.3. Heb. 13.18. 1 Kor. 4.4.\x*, kuze kube lamuhla.
\v 2 Kodwa uAnaniya umpristi omkhulu\x + 24.1.\x* walaya labo ababemi phansi kwakhe ukuthi bamtshaye umlomo\x + 1 Kho. 22.24.\x*.
\v 3 UPawuli wasesithi kuye: UNkulunkulu uzakutshaya, mduli oconjwe waba mhlophe\x + Mat. 23.27.\x*; ngoba wena uhlalele ukungahlulela ngomlayo, kanti ngokuphambene lomlayo ulaya ukuthi ngitshaywe\x + Dute. 25.1,2. Joha. 7.51.\x*?
\v 4 Lababemi lapho bathi: Uyamthuka umpristi omkhulu kaNkulunkulu yini\x + Joha. 18.22.\x*?
\v 5 UPawuli wasesithi: Bengingazi, bazalwane, ukuthi ungumpristi omkhulu\x + 24.17.\x*; ngoba kulotshiwe \add ukuthi\add*: Ungakhulumi kubi ngombusi wesizwe sakini\x + Eks. 22.28.\x*.
\v 6 Kwathi uPawuli esekwazi ukuthi enye ingxenye yabo ingabaSadusi\x + Mat. 22.23.\x*, lenye ingabaFarisi, wamemeza emphakathini\x + 22.30.\x* \add wathi\add*: Madoda bazalwane, mina ngingumFarisi, indodana yomFarisi\x + 26.5. Fil. 3.5.\x*; ngethemba langokuvuka kwabafileyo mina ngiyahlulelwa\x + 24.21. 24.15. 26.6-8. 28.20. Tit. 2.13.\x*.
\v 7 Kwathi esetshilo lokhu, kwavela ukuphikisana kwabaFarisi labaSadusi\x + Mat. 22.23.\x*, lexuku ladabuka phakathi;
\v 8 ngoba abaSadusi\x + Mat. 22.23.\x* bathi kakukho ukuvuka \add kwabafileyo\add*, loba ingilosi, loba umoya; kodwa abaFarisi bayakuvuma kokubili\x + Mat. 22.23. Mark. 12.18. Luka 20.27.\x*.
\v 9 Kwasekuvela ukumemeza okukhulu; kwathi ababhali behlelo labaFarisi basukuma baphika kakhulu besithi: Kasitholi bubi kulumuntu\x + 23.29.\x*; kodwa nxa umoya kumbe ingilosi kukhulume laye\x + 22.7,17,18.\x*, kasingalwi simelene loNkulunkulu\x + 5.39.\x*.
\v 10 Kwathi sekuvele ukuphikisana okukhulu, induna enkulu yesaba ukuthi uPawuli uzadatshulwa yibo, yalaya amabutho\x + 23.27. Luka 23.11.\x* ukuthi ahle amhluthule phakathi kwabo\x + 23.15. 21.35. 22.30.\x*, njalo abuyele laye enkambeni yamabutho\x + 23.16,32. 21.34.\x*.
\v 11 Njalo ngobusuku obulandelayo iNkosi yema phansi kwakhe\x + 18.9. 27.23,24. 22.14.\x* yathi: Mana isibindi Pawuli; ngoba njengalokhu ufakaze\x + 22.15.\x* izinto ngami eJerusalema\x + Luka 16.28.\x*, kunjalo-ke umele ufakaze leRoma\x + 19.21.\x*.
\s Iqhinga lamaJuda lokubulala uPawuli
\p
\v 12 Kwathi sekusile, abanye bamaJuda benza iqhinga, bazibopha ngesiqalekiso, besithi kabayikudla lokunatha baze bambulale uPawuli\x + 23.21,30. 25.3. 9.24.\x*.
\v 13 Njalo babengaphezu kwamatshumi amane abenza lesisifungo ndawonye;
\v 14 abaya kubapristi abakhulu labadala bathi: Sizibophe ngesiqalekiso esikhulu\x + Luka 22.15.\x*, sokuthi kasiyikudla lutho size simbulale uPawuli.
\v 15 Ngakho khathesi lina kanye lomphakathi\x + 22.30.\x* yazisani induna enkulu, ukuze imthume kini kusasa\x + 23.10.\x*, ngokungathi lizazwisisa okunengi ngendaba zakhe; thina-ke, engakasondeli, sesilungele ukumbulala\x + 23.20. 18.25,26. 24.22.\x*.
\v 16 Kodwa indodana kadadewabo kaPawuli yezwa ngokumcathamela, yeza yangena enkambeni yamabutho\x + 23.10.\x*, yamtshela uPawuli.
\v 17 UPawuli wasebizela kuye enye yezinduna zekhulu wathi: Sana lelijaha enduneni enkulu; ngoba lilento elizayitshela yona.
\v 18 Yasilithatha-ke yalisa enduneni enkulu, yasisithi: UPawuli isibotshwa ungibizele kuye wacela ukuthi ngilethe lelijaha kuwe, lilento elizakutshela yona.
\v 19 Induna enkulu yasilithatha ngesandla, yasibuyela eceleni bebodwa, yabuza: Kuyini ozongitshela khona?
\v 20 Laselisithi: AmaJuda avumelene ukucela kuwe\x + 23.14,15.\x*, ukuze wehlisele uPawuli emphakathini kusasa\x + 22.30.\x*, kungathi azahlolisisa\x + 23.14,15.\x* ngcono ulutho ngaye\x + 23.20. 18.25,26. 24.22.\x*.
\v 21 Ngakho wena ungavunyiswa yiwo; ngoba amadoda adlula amatshumi amane kuwo amcathamele\x + Luka 11.54.\x*, azibophe ngesiqalekiso\x + 23.12.\x* ngokuthi angadli anganathi aze ambulale; lakhathesi alungile elindele isithembiso sakho.
\v 22 Ngakho induna enkulu yasiliyekela ijaha lahamba, i\add li\add*laya \add isithi\add*: Ungatsheli muntu ukuthi ungibikele lezizinto\x + 1.4. 17.3. Eks. 18.4. Seb. 23.24.\x*.
\s UPawuli usiwa eKesariya
\p
\v 23 Yasibizela kuyo induna zekhulu ezithile ezimbili, yathi: Lungisani abebutho abangamakhulu amabili ukuze bahambe baze bayefika eKesariya\x + 23.33. 8.40.\x*, labagadi bamabhiza abangamatshumi ayisikhombisa, labemikhonto abangamakhulu amabili, kusukela ngehola lesithathu lobusuku;
\v 24 lungisani lezinyamazana, ukuze ligadise uPawuli limfikise ephephile kumbusi\x + 23.26,33,34. Mat. 27.2.\x* uFelike;
\v 25 wabhala incwadi imumethe lokhu:
\v 26 Klawudiyosi Lisiya kumhlekazi\x + Luka 1.3.\x* umbusi uFelike\x + 23.26,33,34. Mat. 27.2.\x* \add ngiya\add*bingelela\x + 15.23.\x*.
\v 27 Lindoda ibibanjwe ngamaJuda, njalo ibisizabulawa yiwo\x + 21.32,33,24.\x*, ngafika lamabutho ngayophula\x + 23.10.\x*, sengizwile ukuthi ungumRoma\x + 22.25-29.\x*.
\v 28 Ngathi ngifuna ukuthi ngazi isizatho ayimangalela ngaso\x + 19.38.\x*, ngayehlisela\x + 22.30.\x* emphakathini wawo\x + 22.30.\x*;
\v 29 engathi ngithola ukuthi imangalelwe\x + 19.38.\x* ngemibuzo yomlayo wawo\x + 18.15. 25.19.\x*, kodwa ingamangalelwanga ngalutho olufanele ukufa\x + 26.31. 25.25. 23.9.\x* loba izibopho.
\v 30 Kwathi sekuvelile kimi\x + 23.20.\x* ukuthi kwasekuzakuba khona iqhinga ngalindoda ngamaJuda, ngahle nga\add yi\add*thuma kuwe\x + 9.24.\x*, ngibalayile futhi abamangaleli ukuthi bakhulume izinto ababemelene layo ngazo phambi kwakho\x + 23.35. 24.8.\x*. Sala kuhle\x + 15.29.\x*.
\v 31 Abebutho-ke, njengokulaywa kwabo, bamthatha uPawuli, bamusa eAntipatri ngobusuku.
\v 32 Njalo kusisa, batshiya abagadi bamabhiza ukuthi bahambe laye\x + 23.23.\x*, babuyela enkambeni yamabutho\x + 23.10.\x*;
\v 33 okwathi sebefikile eKesariya\x + 23.33. 8.40.\x*, bamnika umbusi incwadi\x + 23.26,33,34. Mat. 27.2.\x*, bammisa loPawuli phambi kwakhe.
\v 34 Kwathi umbusi eseyifundile \add incwadi\x + 23.26,33,34. Mat. 27.2.\x*\add*, wasebuza ukuthi ungowawuphi umkhono\x + 25.1.\x*; esezwile ukuthi ungoweKilikhiya\x + 21.39.\x*,
\v 35 wathi: Ngizakuzwa, sebefikile labamangaleli bakho\x + 23.30.\x*. Waselaya ukuthi alondolozwe endlini kaHerodi\x + Mat. 2.1. Seb. 12.19.\x* yokwahlulela\x + Mat. 27.27.\x*.
